node.detail_zh: 患者從印度抵港，7 月 16 日出現症狀，與第 #2628 及 #2630 宗個案患者有關連，由檢疫中心送院。
node.detail_en: The patient arrived in Hong Kong from India, developed symptoms on July 16, and was transferred to hospital from the quarantine centre. Her case is epidemiologically related to the cases of patients #2628 and #2630.
